{"tid":1219194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【義士須知】勿信保險Agent狗亂填Claim Form","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:04:46.000Z","uid":11462,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6a4eb287d714aae157a2a81f4daca579046f396b","tid":1219194,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"好多義士受傷，食哂催淚彈、水劑，撤退仆親跌親，甚至比狗射傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睇到有啲Post都有巴打問保險Claim唔Claim到，但係無咩回應。但嘔心就係Facebook彈好多Agent狗share保險比較網站、產品條款出嚟發災難財食人血饅頭，叫人「搵下佢」問下點同醫生講傷勢、點講事後經過，點去Claim錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2dxWwy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2dxWwy.png&h=b6c90ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66NiRXA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66NiRXA.png&h=bf3c3a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母啦！Shaco Chau</span></span><br />\n<br />\n間間公司唔同產品都有唔同Exclusion，唔係到深究。但保險最基本原則就係最高誠信，不論投保、索償都要提供所有正確無誤資料。<br />\n<br />\n以前有一單案例 HKSAR v Man Choi Wai DCCC572/13<br />\n新聞Link <a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20131023/00412_004.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20131023%2F00412_004.html&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a3929279\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20131023/00412_004.html</a><br />\n因為老母填Claim form虛構女兒去世前一日行程，被Claim Department發現報警，告入欺詐。<br />\n<br />\n識開單唔係大哂，唔好以為考到個IIQE Paper 1,2,3就真係當自己係專業人士先得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個原理好簡單，不保事項最多係Reject Claim。虛假陳述係刑事同可能被保險公司踢單。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎其他真行家（Back office同事或專業既Agent/Broker)甚至係醫務人員、法律人員比下意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要，香港加油</span>"},{"pid":"829439551f506cb47440d4bf17b7ba66ed7930c2","tid":1219194,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"印象中暴動好似不受保"},{"pid":"d8e06b39a985c0ee7ca6a62f18c942e17a0e258b","tid":1219194,"uid":11462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"829439551f506cb47440d4bf17b7ba66ed7930c2","tid":1219194,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:21:33.000Z","msg":"印象中暴動好似不受保"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:41:47.000Z","msg":"無錯，其實好多產品都係不保事項。有行家話有得加Rider，但未必適用係醫療單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeneral Insurance 有項Strikes, Riots and Civil Commotions Clause，可以加上去。不過始終係Commercial既範疇。<br />\n<br />\n至於Group Medical，就睇Broker有無能力fight到落呢個clause。"},{"pid":"3aa3d61bfe14771c4960c62a591fe13a0b4e58a5","tid":1219194,"uid":112205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:43:20.000Z","msg":"高質post 有良心行家"},{"pid":"7c20ad67a0f5d3c499d2ebf943aed1e070ae74a0","tid":1219194,"uid":112205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3aa3d61bfe14771c4960c62a591fe13a0b4e58a5","tid":1219194,"uid":112205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:43:20.000Z","msg":"高質post 有良心行家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"有義士想問點claim 可以搵我睇保單<br />\n<br />\n利申：宏字頭"},{"pid":"5aeaa0c489901e43e6f6779ce8faa2f01b029727","tid":1219194,"uid":11462,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c20ad67a0f5d3c499d2ebf943aed1e070ae74a0","tid":1219194,"uid":112205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3aa3d61bfe14771c4960c62a591fe13a0b4e58a5","tid":1219194,"uid":112205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sc