ry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a20e3bb844d97bcdfcb9727bba12140204cbbd0","tid":1219194,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b066c18a24d16692dd3372d73344cc862c645386","tid":1219194,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db6a14637766effe5857aead75c5c8651f35d2c","tid":1219194,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"香港警察 社會垃圾<br />\n底層散仔毅進弱智仔<br />\n就算大學學歷都係垃圾科，無得揀先去做警犬嘅廢柴，蛇鼠一窩￼￼￼￼"},{"pid":"d40649f75904ea8bfe725434ddfc96c7d4154cb6","tid":1219194,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:10:08.000Z","msg":"唔好為咗嗰少少錢去試claim保險，陣間賠了夫人又折兵"},{"pid":"50d4e5ed298679562d80874a518b5bb9115208a6","tid":1219194,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"其實claim保險係無問題<br />\n<br />\n受傷原因理論上都係任病人up，因為真係考證唔到，你擦損隻腳，邊個知你係比狗追跌倒，定踢波整親？<br />\n<br />\n保險公司亦都唔會查，亦查唔到"},{"pid":"7d49c6b8d625dafa20f28112ce0a8bacf7595205","tid":1219194,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"保險form有部分係醫生填，醫生都係信病人講野，唔通醫生自己查你有無去過金鐘咩<br />\n<br />\n但係虛報的確有機會影響日後索償<br />\n<br />\n假設，有朝一日政府宣佈警察鎮壓係唔合法，會賠償比示威者，咁你就無左個索償既權利啦<br />\n<br />\n但有可能咩？<br />\n<br />\nanyway , 睇醫生唔使講病情外既事"},{"pid":"14761fcf574207eec55aadaafc3f8cc622a9e2ea","tid":1219194,"uid":11462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d4e5ed298679562d80874a518b5bb9115208a6","tid":1219194,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"其實claim保險係無問題<br />\n<br />\n受傷原因理論上都係任病人up，因為真係考證唔到，你擦損隻腳，邊個知你係比狗追跌倒，定踢波整親？<br />\n<br />\n保險公司亦都唔會查，亦查唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:54:54.000Z","ms